ydration solution may help attenuate the electrolyte abnormalities and hypovolemia.', 'Antagonism', 'Caution is advised when bowel cleansing preparations are prescribed in patients treated with agents that can lower the seizure threshold.', 'Moderate', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/111831/', '', 'Alvimopan, Sorbitol, Naloxegol, Bisacodyl, Naldemedine, Methylnaltrexone, Lactitol, Magnesium oxide, Prucalopride, Linaclotide, Magnesium carbonate, More', '', 1767369485);
